 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cylant>Cylant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/18/01 2:10:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Can't Fear Pets on RZ?</span><hr size=1> I've never been able to fear a pet on rallos.  I always just kick the pet, and fear dosn't even get resisted or anything.. it just dosn't work. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/18/01 3:02:36 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Kambic/TRINITY.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Can't Fear Pets on RZ?</span><hr size=1> Ok well I have heard conflicting stories, all I know is that I kicked that guy, it hit him, it said he was feared, he turned his back, it wore off, and we were fighting again...<br>
